If optional WITH-DISTANCE is non-nil then return (TAG COMMITS)
where COMMITS is the number of commits in TAG but not in \"HEAD\"."
  (--when-let (magit-git-string "describe" "--contains" "HEAD")
    (save-match-data
      (when (string-match "^[^^~]+" it)
